怀孕。 视频截图 对此，辖区派出所工作人员称，公安机关已经处理了，但未透露具体情况。 瑞幸咖啡客服表示，没有接收到相关通知，门店是正常营业的。涉事咖啡店工作人员称，该店长已经离职。「17 岁女孩被诱骗致两次怀孕后自杀」，警方回应 _ 胡某 _ 李先生 _ 瑞幸"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-dbe20e536044c65364663b688bea87e1_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "377 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665787016"}}, "attached_info": "CkAItoCD7Izb27h6EAMaCTExMDIzMDMzOSDLh8q2BjAAONoCQAJyCTY2NTc4NzAxNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1725159346.147777", "card_id": "Q_665800531", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 78}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "苹果为什么不对 12306 买票抽成?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "12306 买票明显是在 12306 平台上面的内购啊，为什么苹果不抽成 30% 呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/39420a7da_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "302 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665800531"}}, "attached_info": "CkAItoCD7Izb27h6EAMaCTExMDIzMzM3MiCi8sq2BjAAOJMBQANyCTY2NTgwMDUzMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1725159346.148043", "card_id": "Q_665694783", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 133}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "巴西冻结马斯克星链银行账户，马斯克宣布向巴西免费提供互联网服务直至问题解决，这会带来哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "针对 SpaceX 的星链账户被冻结，马斯克 8 月 30 日在社交媒体 X 上发文表示，SpaceX 将免费为巴西用户提供互联网服务，直到问题得到解决。马斯克发文中还表示，许多偏远的学校和医院都依赖于星链卫星网络，虽然公司的账户被冻结了，但我们不想切断任何人的联系。星链账户被封后，马斯克宣布向巴西免费提供互联网服务直至问题解决 _SpaceX_ 公司 _ 社交"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.co